import React from 'react'; const InfoTab = ({ match }) => { if (!match) return
Match info not available.
; const { localteam, visitorteam, venue, toss_won_team, elected, status, note, starting_at, type, league, stage, season, first_umpire, second_umpire, tv_umpire, referee, } = match; const formatDate = (dateStr) => { const date = new Date(dateStr); return date.toLocaleString(); }; return (
Match {localteam?.name} vs {visitorteam?.name}
Status {status} {note && `- ${note}`}
Date & Time {formatDate(starting_at)}
Match Type {type?.toUpperCase()}
League {league?.name}
Stage {stage?.name}
Season {season?.name}
Venue {venue?.name}, {venue?.city}
Toss {toss_won_team?.name} elected to {elected}
Umpires {first_umpire?.fullname || 'N/A'} (on-field), {second_umpire?.fullname || 'N/A'} (on-field), {tv_umpire?.fullname ? ` ${tv_umpire.fullname} (TV),` : ''} {referee?.fullname || 'N/A'} (Referee)
); }; export default InfoTab;
